OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,4,Cmade a lord and UK minister
OL,6,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar has
OL,7,Fbeen made a lord and minister in the
OL,8,FDepartment for Business, Innovation,
OL,9,FScience and Trade, Downing Street has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FLord Sarwar, who has been Scottish
OL,13,FLabour leader since 2021, was among
OL,14,Fthe first to call for Sir Keir Starmer
OL,15,Fto stand down in February.
OL,17,FFirst Minister of Scotland John
OL,18,FSwinney hit out at the "hypocrisy" of
OL,19,Fthe expected appointment earlier on
OL,20,FWednesday.
OL,26,@zD@XOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
