PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784772170
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,4,Cmade a lord and UK minister
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Press Association, the
OL,7,FFirst Minister said: "I think what it
OL,8,Fdemonstrates is an appalling level of
OL,9,Fjudgment by Anas Sarwar.
OL,11,F"He said before the (Holyrood)
OL,12,Felection he had absolutely no interest
OL,13,Fin going to the House of Lords, he
OL,14,Fonly wanted to be first minister of
OL,15,FScotland.
OL,17,F"Then, after the election, Anas Sarwar
OL,18,Fhas accepted a place in the House of
OL,19,FLords ` a body, by the way, he wants
OL,20,Fto abolish.
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784772170
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,4,Cmade a lord and UK minister
OL,6,F"That is an incredible level of
OL,7,Fhypocrisy and it just illustrates what
OL,8,FI think the Prime Minister is trying
OL,9,Fto address, which is the fact that
OL,10,Fpoliticians say one thing one minute
OL,11,Fand then do another thing the next
OL,12,Fminute, when it suits them.
OL,14,F"That, I thought, was what Andy
OL,15,FBurnham was trying to address and to
OL,16,Fsolve.
OL,18,F"But instead, Andy Burnham has
OL,19,Fexacerbated that sentiment within our
OL,20,Fsociety."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
