PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784772170
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,4,Cmade a lord and UK minister
OL,6,FDowning Street announced 47 new
OL,7,Fministerial appointment late on
OL,8,FWednesday night, along with 17 re-
OL,9,Fappointments.
OL,11,FLord Sarwar said: "I am delighted and
OL,12,Fhonoured to have been asked by the
OL,13,FPrime Minister to serve every part of
OL,14,Fthe United Kingdom as the Minister of
OL,15,FState for Trade.
OL,17,F"Throughout my life, I have only ever
OL,18,Fbeen motivated by public service. The
OL,19,Fopportunity to serve our country is
OL,20,Fall I have ever asked.
OL,26,@sD@SOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784772170
OL,3,CScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,4,Cmade a lord and UK minister
OL,6,F"That's why this is an opportunity I
OL,7,Fhumbly accept.
OL,9,F"I've seen how Andy Burnham has worked
OL,10,Fto empower communities, to deliver
OL,11,Fchange, to brings jobs and economic
OL,12,Fgrowth through working with
OL,13,Fbusinesses, to make Manchester a great
OL,14,Fplace to live and do business. We have
OL,15,Fa job of work to do to replicate that
OL,16,Fin every corner of the United Kingdom."
OL,18,FActing leader of the Scottish Labour
OL,19,FParty Jackie Baillie said further
OL,20,Fdetails of the leadership election
OL,21,Fwill be shared in due course.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUxD@gO]
